        public ProcessResult createResult(SaverAnswer jobDone)
        Description copied from interface: ProcessInterface
        Creates a process result from the result of a database

        It is very common, for some parameters managers (like ParametersManager that in a multiexecution context, one thread has already done the job. In this case the the ExecutionRun wants the unknow result and will use this method to have a @link io.tessilab.oss.hypop.results.ProcessResult} who must contain the same fields than the method ProcessInterface.computeIt(io.tessilab.oss.hypop.parameters.execution.ExecutionParametersSet) will have, with the output of the database
